Rate Type

Showing Tee Times for:

Sep 05, 2022
Apply
info

Please note this is an ADULT 18-Hole green fee. JR or SR Rates when available - will be confirmed at the pro-shop and adjusted when government issued photo identification is presented. Tee times are limited to ONE FOURSOME PER GOLFER EACH DAY the person reserving the tee time must a player within the reservation. Additional tee-time bookings will be cancelled by the pro-shop and your online booking privileges may be suspended. If you need to cancel or modify your tee time, you must call the Riverway Pro Shop at 604-280-4653 or Burnaby Mountain Pro Shop at 604-280-7355  to avoid any charges to your credit card. You are welcome to call the Pro Shop to check for any cancellations in the upcoming 2 day period including the same day. Thank you!

Additional tee-time bookings will be cancelled by the pro-shop and your online booking privileges may be suspended. If you need to cancel or modify your tee time, you must call the Riverway Pro Shop at 604-280-4653 or Burnaby Mountain Pro Shop at 604-280-7355  to avoid any charges to your credit card. You are welcome to call the Pro Shop to check for any cancellations in the upcoming 2 day period including the same day. Thank you!
